title: Economic Development
subtitle: Promoting business growth, attraction, and retention in Aberdeen — your Home of Opportunity.
description: Aberdeen Economic Development Department — business incentives, site selection, permitting guidance, and Chamber of Commerce partnerships.
deptPhone: "(410) 272-1600 ext. 216"
deptRealUrl: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/economic-development"
